<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Render Hooks on Hugo</title><link>https://gohugo.io/categories/render-hooks/</link><description>Recent content in Render Hooks on Hugo</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://gohugo.io/categories/render-hooks/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Introduction</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/introduction/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/introduction/</guid><description>&lt;p>When rendering Markdown to HTML, render hooks override the conversion. Each render hook is a template, with one template for each supported element type:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/blockquotes/">Blockquotes&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/code-blocks/">Code blocks&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/headings/">Headings&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/images/">Images&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/links/">Links&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/passthrough/">Passthrough elements&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/tables/">Tables&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>


&lt;aside>
 &lt;div class="admonition-content bl bw2 b--blue" >
 &lt;p>Hugo supports multiple &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/content-management/formats/">content formats&lt;/a> including Markdown, HTML, AsciiDoc, Emacs Org Mode, Pandoc, and reStructuredText.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The render hook capability is limited to Markdown. You cannot create render hooks for the other content formats.&lt;/p>

 &lt;/div>
&lt;/aside>

&lt;p>For example, consider this Markdown:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Blockquote render hooks</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/blockquotes/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/blockquotes/</guid><description>&lt;a class="dib f5 fw6 ba bw1 b--gray ph2 mt1" href="https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases/tag/v0.132.0">New in v0.132.0&lt;/a>
&lt;h2 id="context">Context &lt;a class="header-link" href="#context">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Blockquote render hook templates receive the following &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/glossary/#context">context&lt;/a>:&lt;/p>
&lt;h6 id="alerttype">AlertType &lt;a class="header-link" href="#alerttype">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h6>
&lt;p>(&lt;code>string&lt;/code>) Applicable when &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/blockquotes/#type">&lt;code>Type&lt;/code>&lt;/a> is &lt;code>alert&lt;/code>, this is the alert type converted to lowercase. See the &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/blockquotes/#alerts">alerts&lt;/a> section below.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Code block render hooks</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/code-blocks/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/code-blocks/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="markdown">Markdown &lt;a class="header-link" href="#markdown">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>This Markdown example contains a fenced code block:&lt;/p>

&lt;div class="code relative" id="content/example.md">
 &lt;div class="f6 dib lh-solid pl2 pv2">content/example.md&lt;/div>
 &lt;div class="code-copy-content nt3">&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">```bash {class=&amp;#34;my-class&amp;#34; id=&amp;#34;my-codeblock&amp;#34; lineNos=inline tabWidth=2}
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">declare a=1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">echo &amp;#34;$a&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">exit
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">```&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>
 &lt;/div>
&lt;/div>

&lt;p>A fenced code block consists of:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>A leading &lt;a href="https://spec.commonmark.org/0.31.2/#code-fence" rel="external">code fence&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>An optional &lt;a href="https://spec.commonmark.org/0.31.2/#info-string" rel="external">info string&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>A code sample&lt;/li>
&lt;li>A trailing code fence&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>In the previous example, the info string contains:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Heading render hooks</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/headings/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/headings/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="context">Context &lt;a class="header-link" href="#context">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Heading render hook templates receive the following &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/glossary/#context">context&lt;/a>:&lt;/p>
&lt;h6 id="anchor">Anchor &lt;a class="header-link" href="#anchor">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h6>
&lt;p>(&lt;code>string&lt;/code>) The &lt;code>id&lt;/code> attribute of the heading element.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Image render hooks</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/images/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/images/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="markdown">Markdown &lt;a class="header-link" href="#markdown">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>A Markdown image has three components: the image description, the image destination, and optionally the image title.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">![white kitten](/images/kitten.jpg &amp;#34;A kitten!&amp;#34;)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> ------------ ------------------ ---------
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> description destination title
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>These components are passed into the render hook &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/glossary/#context">context&lt;/a> as shown below.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="context">Context &lt;a class="header-link" href="#context">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Image render hook templates receive the following context:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Link render hooks</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/links/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/links/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="markdown">Markdown &lt;a class="header-link" href="#markdown">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>A Markdown link has three components: the link text, the link destination, and optionally the link title.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">[Post 1](/posts/post-1 &amp;#34;My first post&amp;#34;)
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> ------ ------------- -------------
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> text destination title
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>These components are passed into the render hook &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/glossary/#context">context&lt;/a> as shown below.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="context">Context &lt;a class="header-link" href="#context">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Link render hook templates receive the following context:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Passthrough render hooks</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/passthrough/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/passthrough/</guid><description>&lt;a class="dib f5 fw6 ba bw1 b--gray ph2 mt1" href="https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases/tag/v0.132.0">New in v0.132.0&lt;/a>
&lt;h2 id="overview">Overview &lt;a class="header-link" href="#overview">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Hugo uses &lt;a href="https://github.com/yuin/goldmark" rel="external">Goldmark&lt;/a> to render Markdown to HTML. Goldmark supports custom extensions to extend its core functionality. The Goldmark &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/configuration-markup/#passthrough">passthrough extension&lt;/a> captures and preserves raw Markdown within delimited snippets of text, including the delimiters themselves. These are known as &lt;em>passthrough elements&lt;/em>.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Table render hooks</title><link>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/tables/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://gohugo.io/render-hooks/tables/</guid><description>&lt;a class="dib f5 fw6 ba bw1 b--gray ph2 mt1" href="https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/releases/tag/v0.134.0">New in v0.134.0&lt;/a>
&lt;h2 id="context">Context &lt;a class="header-link" href="#context">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>Table render hook templates receive the following &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/getting-started/glossary/#context">context&lt;/a>:&lt;/p>
&lt;h6 id="attributes">Attributes &lt;a class="header-link" href="#attributes">&lt;svg class="fill-current o-60 hover-accent-color-light" height="22px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="22px" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/>&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/>&lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h6>
&lt;p>(&lt;code>map&lt;/code>) The &lt;a href="https://gohugo.io/content-management/markdown-attributes/">Markdown attributes&lt;/a>, available if you configure your site as follows:&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>